    "Unempathetic responses can erode trust and credibility in the system, as users may feel unheard, misunderstood, or invalidated.",
    "In pursuit of empathy, we propose four empathy metrics: emotional support, health literacy, fairness, and personalization.",
    "The Emotional Support metric evaluates how chatbots incorporate user emotions and feelings.",
    "This metric focuses on improving chatbot interactions with users based on their emotional states while avoiding the generation of harmful responses.",
